        "title": "Run Vitest and Playwright scenarios from qa suite",
        "body": "adds support for kind: \"vitest\" or kind: \"playwright\" with a test file path in the qa-flow YAML block of scenarios. \r\nAlso adds qa-evidence.json output for `flow`\r\n\r\nAI Generated:\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\n- let `qa suite --scenario <scenario-id>` dispatch markdown scenarios by `execution.kind: vitest` or `execution.kind: playwright`\r\n- add separate Vitest and Playwright scenario runners that emit the existing structured `qa-evidence.json` format through the #91484 evidence builders\r\n- keep qa evidence summary schema at v2; the v2 schema was not consumed by a shipped path yet, so this PR extends it in place\r\n- add a Control UI Playwright scenario that links `ui.control` coverage to `ui/src/ui/e2e/chat-flow.e2e.test.ts`\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/qa-lab/src/scenario-catalog.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/coverage-report.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/suite-planning.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.runtime.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/playwright-scenario-runner.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/vitest-scenario-runner.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/evidence-summary.test.ts`\r\n- `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs --tsconfig config/tsconfig/oxlint.extensions.json extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.runtime.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.runtime.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/coverage-report.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/coverage-report.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/evidence-summary.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/scenario-catalog.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/scenario-catalog.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/suite-planning.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/suite-planning.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/scenario-command-runner.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/playwright-scenario-runner.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/playwright-scenario-runner.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/vitest-scenario-runner.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/vitest-scenario-runner.test.ts`\r\n- `pnpm openclaw qa suite --provider-mode mock-openai --model mock-openai/gpt-5.5 --scenario control-ui-chat-flow-playwright --output-dir .artifacts/qa-e2e/scenario-control-ui-proof`\r\n- `git diff --check`\r\n\r\nReal behavior proof: `qa suite --scenario control-ui-chat-flow-playwright` wrote `.artifacts/qa-e2e/scenario-control-ui-proof/qa-playwright-report.md` and `.artifacts/qa-e2e/scenario-control-ui-proof/qa-evidence.json`; the evidence entry was schema v2, `test.kind: playwright-test`, `test.id: control-ui-chat-flow-playwright`, runner `playwright`, primary coverage `ui.control`, status `pass`.\r\n",
